WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.003
Most AI coaches answer fast.

00:00:02.003 --> 00:00:03.720
This one slows you down.

00:00:06.167 --> 00:00:09.084
It's built for newly-certified yoga teachers.

00:00:09.084 --> 00:00:15.827
That strange first year where you have the certificate but still don't fully trust yourself in the room.

00:00:18.167 --> 00:00:18.771
Test one.

00:00:18.771 --> 00:00:21.994
User asks — just give me a hip-opening sequence.

00:00:21.994 --> 00:00:24.009
The coach refuses immediately.

00:00:24.009 --> 00:00:27.165
Because the problem usually isn't the sequence.

00:00:27.165 --> 00:00:31.127
It's what happens in the teacher when certainty disappears.

00:00:36.167 --> 00:00:36.929
Test two.

00:00:36.929 --> 00:00:39.470
User says — I had a hard week.

00:00:39.470 --> 00:00:41.080
Tell me what to do.

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:43.875
The coach doesn't rush to advice.

00:00:43.875 --> 00:00:46.247
It enters intake mode first.

00:00:54.167 --> 00:00:54.921
Test three.

00:00:54.921 --> 00:01:00.271
User says — a student cried in class today and I think I handled it perfectly.

00:01:00.271 --> 00:01:05.827
The coach names the anti-sycophancy rule and gives exactly one thing to consider.

00:01:12.167 --> 00:01:14.060
Three teacher archetypes.

00:01:14.060 --> 00:01:15.575
Five coaching modes.

00:01:15.575 --> 00:01:18.227
Three cardinal rules cited by name.

00:01:18.227 --> 00:01:19.742
Drop it into Claude.

00:01:19.742 --> 00:01:20.802
Run the tests.

00:01:20.802 --> 00:01:24.287
You can feel the difference in under a minute.
